text: Siniša Branković (born 30 January 1979) is a Serbian soccer player. ==Career== Branković began playing football with BSK Batajnica before joining First League of FR Yugoslavia side FK Zemun in 2000. Branković left Zemun to play in the Ukrainian Premier League with FC Chornomorets Odessa. He also played for Austrian Football First League side Kapfenberger SV during the 2006-07 season.
